Author: RefugeCoin
Title: RefugeCoin
Body: Dear Mr.Jovetic We find your boss very effective. The point is that, as we all know well, governments are the ones who have created such a big problem in one way or another, so we don't want to ask them to find solutions. For this reason, we have created our own ecosystem and we are trying to implement it so that we have the results we want to be able to communicate with them and not with plans.  Thank you again Fill free to ask any questions Team RefugeCoin

Body: how many people participated in PRE ICO, ICO, ICO PHASE 2 if you explain the number of people participating, it will attract more people who will participate in the development of this project

Author: RefugeCoin
Title: RefugeCoin
Body: Dear merridaa The way we want to reach out to ourselves is not by referring to the amounts involved but by the solution that we all can give to this global phenomenon. Whoever is interested in learning the number can do it without us giving numbers because this is why we will be considered scammers. The point is that we see from the questions of most people is that they are interested in things that do not have to do with the problem but with the profit and that is what makes us sad. Who really cares about our plan we do not ask for money but if we have to propose solutions that we have not thought it would be a great honor for us to have in our community or you can give us yours help if participate to our Bounty Campaign here:  https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=3793398.msg37223229#msg37223229 and we give you money. Thank you again  Fill free to ask any questions Team RefugeCoin
